{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_10_01_short",
  "title": "井川葵 1話 「そばにいる」 (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "葵、『情熱だけで生きてみろ』の\nMVの撮影日程、メールで送ったけど確認したか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi‚ about “Try Living on Passion Alone”—\nI sent you the MV shooting schedule by email. Did you check it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "確認してあるよ\nそれにしても、初披露からだいぶ時間が空いたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I checked it.\nStill‚ it’s been quite a while since we first performed it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 13.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "『Grab the BIG4』で曲を披露したのは\n随分前だよ。もっと早くやれば良かったのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The time we performed it at “Grab the BIG4” was\nway back. We should’ve done this sooner.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "あの曲はいつリリースするの、って\n会う人みんなに言われて困ってるんだけどな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Honestly‚ everyone I meet keeps asking me\nwhen we’ll release that song— it’s getting awkward.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.666666158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 25.766666158
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そもそも『Grab the BIG4』で\nあの曲を披露する予定はなかったからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To begin with‚ during “Grab the BIG4”—\nWe didn’t even plan to perform that song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.266666158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 31.2999994914
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "そうだっけ。んー、そうだったかもね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? Hmm‚ yeah‚ maybe you’re right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.2999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 35.2999994914
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "だからMV撮影の準備なんてしてなかったんだよ\nそれにBIG4になってすぐ、海外ツアーに行っただろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why we hadn’t prepared for the MV shoot.\nAnd right after you became BIG4‚ you went on an overseas tour.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.9999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "レコーディングだって、ついこの間済ませたばかりだ\nむしろ早かったと思ってほしいくらいだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚ the recording was only finished recently.\nIf anything‚ I’d say that was actually pretty fast.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.5333328247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 49.4333328247
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "そっか。{user}君は、最速で撮影を\n組んでくれたんだね。じゃあ、ありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. You arranged the shoot\nas quickly as possible‚ huh? Then‚ thank you for that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.766666158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_10_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ苦労はしたが、それが俺の仕事だからな\nところで、俺からも一つ、質問をいいか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It took some effort‚ but that’s my job.\nBy the way‚ can I ask you something‚ too?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.0333328247,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}